) in New York City is a reputable ESL school, offering programs ranging from beginner to advanced English levels.\r\n\r\nMEC is accredited by the Commission on English Language Program Accreditation (CEA) and licensed by the Bureau of Proprietary School Supervision (BPSS). Additionally, the school is authorized under federal law to enroll nonimmigrant students.\r\n\r\nFor tourists visiting the United States on a B1\/B2 visa, MEC offers a semi-intensive ESL program. This program allows visitors to legally study English in the US as long as the course is non-degree and part-time.\r\n\r\nif you want to know about <a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/student-life-in-usa-all-challenges-and-opportunities\/\">student life in usa<\/a> read this article:\r\n\r\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"O7uu3IUtio\"><a href=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/student-life-in-usa-all-challenges-and-opportunities\/\">Student Life in USA | ALL Challenges and Opportunities<\/a><\/blockquote><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; visibility: hidden;\" title=\"&#8220;Student Life in USA | ALL Challenges and Opportunities&#8221; &#8212; Abroadin \" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/student-life-in-usa-all-challenges-and-opportunities\/embed\/#?secret=z6YknjCni3#?secret=O7uu3IUtio\" data-secret=\"O7uu3IUtio\" width=\"500\" height=\"282\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"><\/iframe>\r\n\r\n<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-2596 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/beautiful-woman-with-american-flag-independence-day-1-scaled.webp\" alt=\"study english in the us\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/beautiful-woman-with-american-flag-independence-day-1-scaled.webp 2560w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/