gram with 12 hours per week, the Everyday English Program with 8 hours per week, and Weekend English with 4 hours per week on Saturdays.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>17. New York Language Center LLC, Manhattan, Study English in the US<\/h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.nylanguagecenter.com\/manhattan-upper-west-side\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Location:<\/strong> New York City<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Duration:<\/strong> 1 &#8211; 26 weeks<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Classes per week:<\/strong> 16<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Age Range:<\/strong> 15 &#8211; 99 years old<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Starting Cost:<\/strong> $270<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\nNYLC Manhattan is close to Central Park, Columbia University, and Riverside Park, with Times Square and Midtown Manhattan only 15 minutes away by subway.\r\n\r\nThe programs at this location include the Intensive Language Program, which offers 20 hours of instruction per week, and the Semi-Intensive Program with 16 hours per week. Part-time options are also available, including an ESL Part-Time Program with 12 hours per week and private lessons for more personalized instruction.\r\n\r\nClasses are held from Monday to Thursday, with sessions available both in the morning and evening.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>18. International Language Institute, Learn English in the USA<\/h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/ilidc.com\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Location:<\/strong> Washington DC<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Duration:<\/strong> 1 &#8211; 52 weeks<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Classes per week:<\/strong> 25<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Age Range:<\/strong> 14 years old and older<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Starting Cost:<\/strong> $280<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\nSince 1970, the International Language Institute (ILI) has provided exceptional English instruction to students worldwide. ILI is committed to delivering quality language education and the necessary support services for effective study in the United States.\r\n\r\nILI provides 12 levels of English classes, from beginner to university level, and includes access to a computer room with the Internet, weekly student activities, counseling, and assistance with college applications.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>19. American English Center Miami Beach, Studying English in the USA<\/h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/aenglishcenter.com\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Location:<\/strong> Miami Beach<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Duration:<\/strong> 1 &#8211; 24 weeks<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Classes per week:<\/strong> 15<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Age Range:<\/strong> 18 years old and older<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Starting Cost:<\/strong> $280<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\nAmerican English Center Miami Beach provides a 15-hour-per-week English program for those looking to learn the language in a short time. It caters to students with B1\/B2 visas, ESTA, or non-F1 visas and offers beginner, intermediate, and advanced levels.\r\n\r\nThe course duration ranges from 1 to 24 weeks, with class days from Monday to Thursday. Morning sessions run from 09:00 AM to 01:30 PM, and while the schedule may change depending on availability and season, you can expect a small class size averaging six students, with a maximum of ten.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>20. Mentor Language Institute, Hollywood Campus, Learn English in the USA<\/h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n \t<li><a href=\"https:\/\/mliesl.edu\/hollywood\/\">Official Website<\/a><\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Location:<\/strong> Hollywood, Los Angeles<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Duration:<\/strong> 1 &#8211; 52 weeks<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Classes per week:<\/strong> 18<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Age Range:<\/strong> 18 years old and older<\/li>\r\n \t<li><strong>Starting Cost:<\/strong> $293t<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\nMentor Language Institute offers classes run from Monday to Thursday with morning sessions from 09:00 AM to 01:15 PM, offering 18 lessons per week. The institute operates year-round with flexible start dates throughout the year.\r\n\r\nEach class typically accommodates an average of 8 students. At the end of the course, students receive a certificate of completion, validating their English language proficiency and academic achievement at Mentor Language Institute.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h2>Final Thoughts<\/h2>\r\nThis was the hand-picked list of the best and lowest-cost courses for studying English in the USA in the coming years. If you found this post helpful, explore more related content on Abroadin&#8217;s blog. Feel free to ask your questions below\u2014our experts are here to guide you through your journey to a bright future!\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-71ab65a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"71ab65a\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;jet_parallax_layout_list&quot;:[]}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-0e96210\" data-id=\"0e96210\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e10c4f3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e10c4f3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.23.0 - 05-08-2024 *\/\n.elementor-heading-title{padding:0;margin:0;line-height:1}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title[class*=elementor-size-]>a{color:inherit;font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-small{font-size:15px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.ele